snippet.textDisplay: This Emma should take a look in her home country. The US is treating covid as over but about 300 to 500 americans are still dying everyday with tens of thousands of new cases everyday. The cases and deaths in China is way less (about a total of 500 deaths this 2022) but their government is taking this very seriously.
